Count matching messages

Usage: mxr count [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>  

Options:
      --mode <MODE>      [possible values: lexical, hybrid, semantic]
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
